{"tid":2464335,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"富途牛牛 新功能 - 自選組合 (portfolio tracker)","createTime":"2021-03-27T11:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T11:19:13.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c80155df0e5bae5231a005bc2af9a9d679af31","tid":2464335,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T11:14:39.000Z","msg":"1、什麼是組合？<br />\n富途模擬組合支持創建港股、美股、A股的跨市場分散組合，可以有效降低投資品種相關性，快速便捷地對一籃子股票進行操作，能更直觀地反映您的投資思路，幫助您更好地把握投資機會。<br />\n<br />\n2、如何玩轉組合<br />\n<br />\n通過創建組合或者查看他人創建組合，進入組合詳情頁。在這裡，您可以：<br />\n<br />\n1）關注您喜歡的組合，可以在組合列表頁管理關注組合，掌握關注組合動態<br />\n2）編輯組合基本信息，創建組合簡介或記錄自己投資思路<br />\n3）查看組合倉位信息，了解組合持倉股票及比例<br />\n4）查看組合市場及行業分布情況，把控創建人的投資方向<br />\n5）對持倉股票進行調倉，並查看調倉記錄（僅限自建組合）<br />\n6）分享與評論組合，將優秀組合與他人共享或在牛牛圈中參與討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pubimg-10000538.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/202102040289537796536aa70d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubimg-10000538.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com%2F202102040289537796536aa70d8.png&h=4a1c3cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pubimg-10000538.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/2021020402895378064b0550e6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubimg-10000538.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com%2F2021020402895378064b0550e6d.png&h=4e2dbc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pubimg-10000538.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/2021020402895379435366af795.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubimg-10000538.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com%2F2021020402895379435366af795.png&h=ee69927d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家砌自己既心水組合再分享上牛牛圈同牛友一齊討論啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/150646432_3668782759907657_6280427529746579097_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=xmn6hstCCMgAX-od7rT&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=1baff4ab4630138acf26ba0ebdb1096b&amp;oe=60869EB3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsco